00:31:11.519 --> 00:31:15.519
A person needed to make money and live a lavish life.

00:31:15.519 --> 00:31:23.519
So that's the life I chose, to study, to get higher education so that I could have what others had.

00:31:24.519 --> 00:31:30.519
